                                                <p>
                                                    ■ Groom yourself! Be sure that you are showered/bathed, your teeth are brushed, hair is neat and
                                                    combed, fingernails are neatly trimmed, you have put on deodorant, and for men, that you have
                                                    shaved on the day of the interview.
                                                </p>
